Package: DeepRHealth
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Medical Code Mapping and Clinical Data Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Zhixia", "Ren",
      email = "jexica0921@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: MA toolkit for standardized medical code lookup, hierarchical
    exploration, and cross-vocabulary mapping (e.g., ICD9CM to CCSCM),
    inspired by the PyHealth framework. Provides tidyverse-compatible
    interfaces for clinical code translation and transformation tasks.
